node.title: Police appeal for information on missing Masterton man
node.description: Police are concerned about a man missing from Masterton since Monday.
node.content:
["Police are concerned about a man missing from Masterton since Monday.", "", "
Missing man Antony Gerard Farrell Photo: Police
", "Antony Gerald Farrell, 52, was last seen on Te Ore Road in the Wairarapa town at 2am.", "Police understand he travelled to the Lake Ferry area.", "Extensive inquires to locate him have been unsuccessful and police are now appealing to the public for help.", "They said Farrell's family were also worried about his welfare.", "He is about 168cm tall and of medium build.", "Police urge anyone with any information regarding Anthony's whereabouts, or to Anthony himself, to call 105."]
